'''''Mystery to Me''''' is an  by /  band , released in 1973 (see ). This was their last album to feature . Most of the songs were penned by guitarist/singer  and keyboardist/singer , who were playing a major role in edging the band's sound towards the radio friendly pop/rock that would make them highly successful a few years later. Although it only sold moderately and produced no hit singles, "Hypnotized" did become an FM radio staple for many years.
